{"tid":2121420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩其實唔係飾物","createTime":"2020-07-23T09:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T09:46:01.000Z","uid":47107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65313d282f9f00686d2e900673f766b543a8665c","tid":2121420,"uid":47107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"全程見到咁樣戴口罩，依家已經叫戴得好d<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkkSc3p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkkSc3p.png&h=3b5ccc28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b97c2f5336cbfbc96e0e76626df15273ed8f4367","tid":2121420,"uid":101733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"未見過啲飾物帶得咁7"},{"pid":"a5bb88db3a941d64f43fa8728671930e69753743","tid":2121420,"uid":304179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"戴口罩掩口不掩鼻同樣違規 籲多洗手<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始亦提到，配戴口罩的定義，是指口罩「要完整覆蓋口同鼻。如果除咗落嚟，或者<span class=\"purple\">戴到個鼻突咗出嚟，已經算觸犯規例</span>。」陳肇始說，政府一直都是因應疫情再作出風險評估，推出不同的防疫政策，一直奉行「張弛有度」的原則。她又指今日是新規例生效首日，會觀察市民對政策的反應，以及實行情況，「如果發現有一些措施，現時未有包含，但唔實施又會有問題的話，我哋都會加入」，又指未來一星期是關鍵時刻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wHzvKbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwHzvKbm.jpg&h=ba59fea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%AE%A4%E5%85%A7%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BB%A4-%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B-%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9C%B2%E9%BC%BB%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E6%9B%B4%E5%9A%B4%E5%8E%B2%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%259C%25B2%25E9%25BC%25BB%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%259A%25B4%25E5%258E